   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>A brother once studied the word calling.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>He put several dozen verses together and grouped them into ten sections.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>For illustration, I will list them in the following sections:</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Section One The source of our calling:</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The primary source God 1 Thes 2:12 .</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The intermediary source Jesus Christ Rom 1:6 .</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Section Two The called ones:</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Scope general all men 1 Cor 1:24 .</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Scope spiritual sinners Luke 5:32 .</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>God's valuation vessels of mercy Rom 9:23-24 .</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Actual condition not many who are wise 1 Cor 1:26 .</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Section Three The goal of our calling:</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Repentance Luke 5:32 .</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Salvation 2 Thes 2:13-14 .</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Peace Col 3:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Light 1 Pet 2:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Fellowship 1 Cor 1:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>Service Rom 1:1 .</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>Freedom Gal 5:13 .</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>Holiness 1 Cor 1:2 .</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>Suffering 1 Pet 2:21 .</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>Eternal life 1 Tim 6:12 .</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>Eternal inheritance Heb 9:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>Eternal glory 1 Pet 5:10 .</S>
   </TEXT>
